dce9dcc943e79212f8b33a9483d7fad737f71ef5","tid":194003,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政治還政治<br />\n睇戲還睇戲呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜都政治化就係中國特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後屌返你政治化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過樹大招風裏面既支那真係無個好人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講支那班官<br />\n寫得好貼地呀"},{"pid":"c4c50267f6bdb9ed95e187b1d6df135b74fb7513","tid":194003,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:31:01.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1343b37dc4523a5f35eea8e461ef7a635f34b27","tid":194003,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:30:21.000Z","msg":"呢套嘢概念上幾得易，<br />\n但我好想睇三條友合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddd5544711bfe23d5cf199916e4a9dde23cd069","tid":194003,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcca10d1eeea1be4cacac68962dadbaf8dd2987","tid":194003,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套嘢概念上幾得易，<br />\n但我好想睇三條友合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實套野拍攝手法唔創新，但香港首次<br />\n例如雲圖，3位導演<br />\n泰國既九路冥婚，9個導演"},{"pid":"d38d9ac2bcf5474556391be8e1c8f28de8be8c66","tid":194003,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢套嘢概念上幾得易，<br />\n但我好想睇三條友合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實套野拍攝手法唔創新，但香港首次<br />\n例如雲圖，3位導演<br />\n泰國既九路冥婚，9個導演</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n杜琪峰套鐵三角都係3個導演 手法仲有趣"},{"pid":"f5e63d54dba681167b86b7b51d70850b4b0b994a","tid":194003,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:16:25.000Z","msg":"套野中國有份合作都block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588279ca800e63346ee0203ae1ac46ab6db4be89","tid":194003,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套野中國有份合作都block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除非舊年套最佳電影，頒俾《智取威虎山》<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}